cations/rest/REST-API-V2.rst#111%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0media-types" class=3D"ext=
ernal-link" rel=3D"nofollow">REST specifications chapter &quot;Media Types&=
quot;</a></p>=20
</div>=20
